461/x5vozxp0d6aqh5ja\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eReal Proof:\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca title=\"https://www.google.cl/search?q=site:vimeo.com+inurl:forgot_password/\u0026amp;num=100\u0026amp;safe=off\u0026amp;client=firefox-a\u0026amp;hs=Ehs\u0026amp;rls=org.mozilla:en-US:official\u0026amp;channel=sb\u0026amp;filter=0\u0026amp;biw=1280\u0026amp;bih=672\" href=\"/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.cl%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dsite%3Avimeo.com%2Binurl%3Aforgot_password%2F%26num%3D100%26safe%3Doff%26client%3Dfirefox-a%26hs%3DEhs%26rls%3Dorg.mozilla%3Aen-US%3Aofficial%26channel%3Dsb%26filter%3D0%26biw%3D1280%26bih%3D672\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://www.google.cl/search?q=site:vimeo.com+inurl:forgot_password/\u0026amp;num=100\u0026amp;safe=off\u0026amp;client=firefox-a\u0026amp;hs=Ehs\u0026amp;rls=org.mozilla:en-US:official\u0026amp;channel=sb\u0026amp;filter=0\u0026amp;biw=1280\u0026amp;bih=672\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e(Please note that this pages are index by Google already )\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis is not a super serious bug I agree.  but still if user don\u0026#39;t change the password this link will be active for some longer time it can be access by Google.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003ePS: it also a good Idea to add /forgot_password/* to \u003ca title=\"http://vimeo.com/robots.txt\" href=\"/redirect?url=http%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2Frobots.txt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttp://vimeo.com/robots.txt\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAny problems reproducing this bug please let me know.\u003c/p\u003e\n","weakness":{"id":57,"name":"Violation of Secure Design Principles"},"original_report_id":null,"original_rep